snippet.title: Catgirl & Doggirl Cafe
snippet.description:
BUY NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1142270/Catgirl__Doggirl_Cafe/

Reborn in a fantasy world you're chosen to open a Japanese-style family restaurant. Instead of buying ingredients, you spend your money rescuing 2 animal-eared girls from a dastardly slaver! Enjoy a heartwarming *tail* about the blossoming romance in the Catgirl & Doggirl Cafe.
